[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大乘六情懺悔",
        "translation": "Great Vehicle Repentance for the Six Faculties",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋元曉撰",
        "translation": "written by Shi Yuanxiao",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c07_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若依法界始遊行者。",
        "translation": "\"Suppose someone begins to wander around according to the Dharma realm.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c08_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於四威儀無一唐遊。",
        "translation": "In the four ways, there's not a single one that he doesn't wander around.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c08_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "念諸佛不思議德。",
        "translation": "He's mindful of the buddhas and doesn't contemplate their virtues.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c08_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常思實相杇銷業障。",
        "translation": "He always reflects on their true characteristics and roots out karmic hindrances.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c09_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普為六道無邊眾生。",
        "translation": "He universally serves the limitless sentient beings of the six destinies.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c09_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "歸命十方無量諸佛。",
        "translation": "They give their lives to measureless buddhas in the ten directions.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c10_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛不異而亦非一。",
        "translation": "The buddhas are not different, yet they are not one.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c10_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一即一切一切即一。",
        "translation": "One is all, and all are one.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c11_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖無所住而無不住。",
        "translation": "Although there's nothing to abide in, there's nothing not to abide in.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c11_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖無所為而無不為。",
        "translation": "Although there's nothing to do, there's nothing not to do.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c12_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一一相好一一毛孔。",
        "translation": "Each one has its own distinctive features, and each one has its own pore.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c12_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遍無邊界盡未來際。",
        "translation": "They pervade the limitless realm and end in the future.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c13_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無障無礙無有差別。",
        "translation": "There are no hindrances, no impediments, and no distinctions.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c13_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "教化眾生無有休息。",
        "translation": "There's no rest when it comes to teaching sentient beings.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c14_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何。",
        "translation": "Why is that?",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c14_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十方三世一塵一念。",
        "translation": "In the ten directions and three times, there's one particle and one thought.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c14_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生死涅槃無二無別。",
        "translation": "Birth-and-death and nirvāṇa are not two, and there's no distinction between them.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c15_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大悲般若不取不捨。",
        "translation": "Great compassionate wisdom doesn't grasp or relinquish.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c15_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以得不共法相應故。",
        "translation": "It's because they attain the mutual correspondence of distinctive qualities.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c16_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今於此處蓮花藏界。",
        "translation": "Here in the lotus-flower treasury realm.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c16_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "盧舍那佛坐蓮花臺。",
        "translation": "Vairocana Buddha is sitting on a lotus-flower dais.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c17_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "放無邊光。",
        "translation": "He radiates an infinite amount of light.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c17_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "集無量眾生。",
        "translation": "He gathers measureless sentient beings.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c17_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "轉無所轉大乘法輪。",
        "translation": "He turns the unvarying great vehicle Dharma wheel.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c18_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩大眾遍滿虛空。",
        "translation": "A great multitude of bodhisattvas fills space.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c18_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受無所受大乘法樂。",
        "translation": "They experience the bliss of the great vehicle dharma that has no place to be experienced.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c19_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而今我等同在於此一實三寶無過之處。",
        "translation": "Now, I'm right here in this place where there's nothing wrong with the single, real Three Treasures.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c19_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不見不聞如聾如盲。",
        "translation": "They don't see or hear, and they're deaf and blind.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c20_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有佛性。",
        "translation": "There's no buddha-nature.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c20_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何為如是。",
        "translation": "Why is it like this?",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c21_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無明顛倒妄作外塵。",
        "translation": "Ignorance is mistaken and deluded, creating external objects.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c21_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "執我我所造種種業。",
        "translation": "They cling to self and what's mine, creating various karmic activities.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c21_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自以覆弊不得見聞。",
        "translation": "They cover themselves with disadvantages and aren't allowed to see and hear.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c22_32",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如餓鬼臨河見火。",
        "translation": "They're like a hungry ghost facing a river and seeing fire.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c22_33",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故今佛前深生慚愧。",
        "translation": "So now, before the Buddha, I'm deeply ashamed.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c23_34",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "發菩提心誠心懺悔。",
        "translation": "He arouse the mind of enlightenment and sincerely repents.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c23_35",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我及眾生無始以來無明所醉。",
        "translation": "'Since beginningless time, I and sentient beings have been drunk with ignorance.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c24_36",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作罪無量。",
        "translation": "We've committed countless sins.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c24_37",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五逆十惡無所不造。",
        "translation": "There's nothing that the five heinous crimes and ten unwholesome kinds of behavior don't create.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c25_38",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自作教他見作隨喜。",
        "translation": "We make ourselves, teach others, and create views that are pleasing to us.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c25_39",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是眾罪不可稱數。",
        "translation": "Such a multitude of sins are incalculable.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c26_40",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛賢聖之所證知。",
        "translation": "They're realized by the buddhas, good men, and sages.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c26_41",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已作之罪深生慚愧。",
        "translation": "The sins they've already committed give rise to a deep sense of shame.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c27_42",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所未作者更不敢作。",
        "translation": "They won't dare to commit those sins that haven't been committed yet.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c27_43",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "□此諸罪實無所有。",
        "translation": "□These sins really don't exist.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c28_44",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眾緣和合假名為業。",
        "translation": "The confluence of many conditions is nominally called karma.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c28_45",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即緣無業離緣亦無。",
        "translation": "They are conditioned by the absence of karma, and they're free from conditioned existence.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c29_46",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非內非外不在中間。",
        "translation": "They're neither internal nor external, and they don't lie in the middle.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0921c29_47",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過去已滅。",
        "translation": "The past has ceased ...",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a01_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未來未生現在無住。",
        "translation": "'s past has ceased ... the future has yet to arise, and the present lacks abiding.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a01_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故所作以其無住故亦無生。",
        "translation": "Therefore, because what's done is unabiding, it's also unarisen.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a01_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先有非生先無誰生。",
        "translation": "What was there before wasn't born, and who was there before won't be born.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a02_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若言本無及與今有。",
        "translation": "If it's said that there was nothing in the past and there is something in the present, then the two meanings are combined and it's called birth.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a02_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二義和合名為生者。",
        "translation": "When the two meanings are combined, it's called birth.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a03_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當本無時即無今有。",
        "translation": "When the original was nonexistent, then there was no present existence.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a03_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當今有時非有本無。",
        "translation": "When there's presently existent, there's not originally nonexistent.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a04_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先後不及有無不合。",
        "translation": "The prior and subsequent aren't compatible with existence and nonexistence.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a04_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二義無合何處有生。",
        "translation": "Where can there be birth when there's no union of the two meanings?",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a05_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "合義既壞散亦不成。",
        "translation": "As the meaning of unity breaks down, dispersion isn't possible.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a05_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不合不散非有非無。",
        "translation": "What's not combined and what's not dispersed is neither existent nor nonexistent.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a06_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無時無有對何為無。",
        "translation": "When there's no existence, what's the opposite of absence?",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a06_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有時無無待誰為有。",
        "translation": "When there's existence, there's nothing, and absence depends on who becomes existence.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a07_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先後有無皆不得成。",
        "translation": "Neither prior nor subsequent existence or nonexistence can come into being.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a07_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知業性本來無生。",
        "translation": "You should know that the nature of karma was originally unarisen.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a08_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從本以來不得有生。",
        "translation": "Since the beginning, there hasn't been any birth.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a08_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當於何處得有無生。",
        "translation": "Where will there be birth or non-birth?",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a09_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有生無生俱不可得。",
        "translation": "Both birth and non-birth are unobtainable.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a09_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "言不可得亦不可得。",
        "translation": "It's said to be unobtainable and unknowable.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a10_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "業性如是諸佛亦爾。",
        "translation": "Thus is the nature of karma, and so are the buddhas.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a10_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如經說言。",
        "translation": "As the sūtra explains, it's like a sentient being who creates actions.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a11_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如眾生造作諸業。",
        "translation": "'It's like a sentient being who creates actions.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a11_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善若惡。",
        "translation": "Whether they're good or bad, they're neither internal nor external.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a11_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非內非外。",
        "translation": "They are neither internal nor external.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a12_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是業性非有非無。",
        "translation": "Thus, the nature of karma is neither existent nor nonexistent.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a12_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦復如是。",
        "translation": "It's also like this.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a12_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "本無今有非無因生。",
        "translation": "What was originally nonexistent now exists and doesn't arise from nonexistence.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a13_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無作無受。",
        "translation": "Nothing is created, and there's no feeling.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a13_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時節和合故得果報。",
        "translation": "It's the result of combining time and seasons.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a13_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行者若能數數思惟如是實相而懺悔者。",
        "translation": "If a practitioner can repeatedly contemplate this truth and repent, he won't be able to do any of the four grave misdeeds.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a14_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四重五逆無所能為。",
        "translation": "The four grave misdeeds and five heinous crimes are impossible to do.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a15_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如虛空不為火燒。",
        "translation": "He's like space that doesn't burn up.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a15_32",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如其放逸無慚無愧。",
        "translation": "As they are, they're careless and lack conscience and modesty.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a16_33",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不能思惟業實相者。",
        "translation": "They can't contemplate the true nature of their actions.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a16_34",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖無罪性將入泥梨。",
        "translation": "Even though it's without a sinful nature, it's about to enter a hell.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a17_35",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如幻虎還吞幻師。",
        "translation": "He's like an illusory tiger that goes back to swallowing an illusory teacher.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a17_36",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故當於十方佛前。",
        "translation": "Therefore, you must appear before the buddhas of the ten directions.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a18_37",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "深生慚愧而作懺悔。",
        "translation": "Deeply conscience and modesty will arise, and you'll make repentance.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a18_38",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作是悔時莫以為作。",
        "translation": "When you make this confession, don't think of it as making it.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a19_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即應思惟懺悔實相所悔之罪既無所有。",
        "translation": "You should then consider the true nature of repentance ... since the sins you repent of don't exist.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a19_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何得有能懺悔者。",
        "translation": "How could there be someone who's able to repent?",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a20_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能悔所悔皆不可得。",
        "translation": "Neither the repentance that's possible nor the repentance that's expressed is obtainable.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a20_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當於何處得有悔法於諸業障作是悔已。",
        "translation": "Where will there be repentance for the karmic hindrances after making this confession?",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a21_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦應懺悔六情放逸。",
        "translation": "They should also repent of the carelessness of the six emotions.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a22_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我及眾生無始已來。",
        "translation": "Since beginningless time, I and sentient beings have never been born.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a22_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不解諸法本來無生。",
        "translation": "We don't understand that all dharmas are originally unarisen.",
        "source": "T45n1908_001:0922a23_7",
